{"word":"H7561 - רָשַׁע - râshaʻ - raw-shah' - Condemn","slug":"H7561","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָשַׁע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>râshaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw-shah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Condemn"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E8;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E2; - ra&#x0302;sha&#x201B;</b> - <i>raw-shah'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>be</i> (causatively <i>do</i> or <i>declare</i>) <i>wrong</i>; by implication to <i>disturb</i>, <i>violate: - </i>condemn, make trouble, vex, be (commit, deal, depart, do) wicked (-ly, -ness)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4849\">H4849</a>, <a href=\"#/H7562\">H7562</a>, <a href=\"#/H7563\">H7563</a>, <a href=\"#/H7564\">H7564</a>"}]}